           <div class="col-lg-6 mt-1 text-center" style="font-family:'Pacifico', cursive;color:#e5eff7;">
               <h1 class="mt-5">Channi Brewing</h1>
               <p class="mt-3 px-5" style="font-size: 20px;">Easy and cheap, channi coffee is great for people who are new to brewing coffee at home and don't have any equipment. All you need is a tea strainer! This method is particularly well-suited for people who are looking to switch from instant coffee but don't want to invest in brewing gear just yet.       
               </p>

